me.wobblyyyy.pathfinder2.zones

Class Zone

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.wobblyyyy.pathfinder2.zones.Zone
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Zone
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A zone is a wrapper for a shape that provides some additional utilities you can make use of. In addition to providing utilities, the Zone class allows you to avoid the Shape class' generics.

    You can overload some methods to control the zone's behavior.

    • onEnter(Pathfinder)
    • onExit(Pathfinder)
    • whileInside(Pathfinder)

    Since:
    0.1.0
    Author:
    Colin Robertson
